message.body: I'm going to see you tomorrow, right? I get out of school at 2pm, but may not head home right away.
Yep. I'll plan on arriving in New York by 2pm. Any suggestions on what to do for parking? Also, I swear that picture you sent looks photoshopped - I'll h
ave to see it to believe it!

Probably least stressful to park in a garage, there's one on my block. free street parking may be hard to find on Friday at that time. DON'T park right in front of my building or you get a nasty ticket...
Ok, I'll plan on using the garage on your block
Check the cost before you commit, I think it should be reasonable, but may depend on how long you think you'll stay. I'll try to get home as soon add I can, but I don't get out tool 2:00
I hate new jersey. But should be there soon
Ok. Garages on my block look like they'll probably run you 25-30 bucks.
